<PageLayout title='关于' {headings} view comment>
  <p>既有缘相识，祝你心想事成</p>
  <p>Now that you have met by fate, I wish you all the best of luck</p>

  {/* general-talk */}
  <h2 id='hobbies'>爱好</h2>
  
