          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>Ghostrunner</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>GTA</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>荒野大镖客</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>泰坦陨落2</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class='mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground'>音游</h4>
        <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2'>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>Phigros</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>Cytus II</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>Lanota</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>Arcaea</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>冰与火之舞</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>节奏医生</span>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>Bits & Bops</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class='mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground'>休闲</h4>
        <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2'>
          <span class='rounded-md border bg-muted px-3 py-1 text-sm'>炉石传说</span>
